The '''Bulgarian Basketball Cup MVP''' is an award that is given to the most outstanding player in the [[Bulgarian Basketball Cup]] tournament. The winner of the award is decide by a panel of the [[Bulgarian Basketball Federation]]. The winner of the award is not necessarily coming from the team that wins the cup title.

