The '''Chandongcha Sports Club''' ([[Chosongul|Chosŏn'gŭl]]: 찬동자체육단; [[Hanja]]: 贊同者體育團) is a [[North Korea]]n [[Association football|football]] club based in [[Chongjin]], [[North Hamgyong]]. They play in the [[DPR Korea League]], the highest football soccer league in North Korea. The team came in first place in 1989. The team plays at [[Chandongcha Park]].

