'''EC Kapfenberg''' is a defunct professional [[ice hockey]] team that played in the [[Austrian Hockey League]]. Based in [[Kapfenberg]], [[Austria]], they were active from 1981 to 2002.<ref>http://www.hockeydb.com/stte/kapfenberg-ec-6303.html</ref>

