{{More footnotes|date=November 2010}} {{Infobox Sport governing body |assocname= International Bodyboarding Association |logo= |sport= Professional [[Bodyboarding]] |abbrev = IBA |founded = |aff = |affdate = |region = |regionyear = |location = |chairman = |chiefexec = |secretary = |coach = |womenscoach = |replaced = |prevfounded = |url = https://apbtour.com/ |countryflag= }}
The '''International Bodyboarding Association''' (IBA) is the governing body for professional [[Bodyboarding|Bodyboarders]] and is dedicated to showcasing the world’s best talent in a variety of progressive formats
It is the IBA which promotes the [[World Tour (bodyboarding)|World Tour]], the international world bodyboarding tour.
