'''Physical disability rugby league''' is a modified version of [[rugby league]] football catered to suit people of various [[physical disability|physical disabilities]].<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/disability-sport/45357094 |title=Warrington Wolves beat South Sydney Rabbtiohs to win PDRL World Club Challenge |publisher=BBC |date=30 August 2018}}</ref>

