{{Infobox football league | logo = | pixels = | country = {{flagicon|SOM}} [[Somalia]] | confed = [[Confederation of African Football|CAF]] | founded = 1967 | teams = 10 | promotion = | relegation = [[Somali Second Division]] | levels = 1 | domest_cup = [[Somalia Cup]] | champions = [[Dekedda FC|Dekedda]] | season = [[2018 Somali First Division|2018]] | tv = [[Somali National Television|SNTV]] | website = [http://www.somsoccer.com/ Official Website] | current = [[2018 Somali First Division]] }}
The '''Somali First Division''' ({{lang-so|Heerka Koowaad ee Soomaali}}, {{lang-ar| دوري الدرجة الأولى الصومالية}}) also known as '''Serie A''', is the Somali professional league for men's [[Association football|football]] association. It has been active for over 48 years since its establishment in 1967.
