[[File:Stadoiiii.jpg|thumb]]
'''Čair Stadium''' ([[Macedonian Cyrillic]]: Стадион Чаир, ''Stadion Čair'') is a multi-use [[stadium]] in the [[Municipality of Čair]] in [[Skopje]], [[Republic of Macedonia]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the formerly home of [[FK Sloga Jugomagnat]] and currently home of [[FK Shkupi]]. The stadium has a capacity of 6000 with 2,800 seats.<ref>http://weltfussballarchiv.com/Stadion.php?ID=184</ref>

